  "body": "If `BlobSidecarsByRoot` returns an exceptional error unrelated to blobs not found, we should either exit or log to propagate the problem downstream. There could be unintended consequences of we don't handle the error correctly\r\n\r\nRelated code:\r\n```go\r\nsidecars, err := s.cfg.BeaconDB.BlobSidecarsByRoot(ctx, root)\r\n\tif err == nil {\r\n\t\tif len(sidecars) >= existingBlobs {\r\n\t\t\tdelete(s.blobNotifier.chanForRoot, root)\r\n\t\t\ts.blobNotifier.Unlock()\r\n\t\t\treturn kzg.IsDataAvailable(kzgCommitments, sidecars)\r\n\t\t}\r\n\t}\r\n```",
